Modifications in this derivative
--------------------------------
Modified by: yfilwzy (https://github.com/yfilwzy)
Date:        2026-06

Key modifications applied on top of the upstream Simprint source:

1. Updater
   - Removed the official Tauri plugin updater (tauri-plugin-updater).
   - Replaced it with a self-developed update channel backed by
     `src-tauri/src/services/updater/` and the standalone
     `src-tauri/src/bin/updater.rs` binary, talking to a user-controlled
     update server instead of the official Tauri endpoints.

2. Proxy chain
   - Added a chain-proxy capability under
     `src-tauri/src/services/proxy_chain/` (subscription parsing,
     Mihomo config generation, process management, node delay testing
     and selection) plus the matching frontend panel
     `plugins/pages/proxy-center/`.

3. Build/runtime hygiene
   - Local runtime configs containing secrets are excluded from version
     control (see .gitignore); only `src-tauri/config.example.toml`
     ships as a placeholder template.


